-stack: vue3 + nuxt + tailwindcss + typescript + firebase
-automatic deploys using vercel and nuxt to sonarmusic.vercel.app


Filter:
  -Genre (local)
  -Jahr (local)
  -Rating (remote)
  -Typ (local)
